data.description:
MOVE IN READY!!  Don't wait for a new Construction home! This Beautiful 2251sqft Basswood Modern Farm House has all the Updates!! Built directly across from a park, with a huge backyard!! 
This home was built with complete open living in mind! As you walk in you are met with a large mudroom open to the dining, living room and Kitchen!! This gorgeous kitchen has quarts countertops and beautiful brass hardware as well as mat black fixtures throughout. 
The main living area boasts of a walk-in pantry and half bath.

The second level is complete with a primary bedroom with vaulted ceiling and on suite bathroom with a quartz double vanity, marble tile floors and large walk in shower. From the bathroom you have an expansive large walk-in-closet!
This level is complete with 3 secondary bedrooms all with walk-in-closets, and a BONUS "Learning Lounge" as well as a full secondary bathroom with beautiful black matte floor tiles which is also presented in the same level laundry room. 

The basement has great potential in adding another 700+sqft of living space which is stubbed for bath, and has an egress window. Enjoy what the community of Edgewater has to offer with its 2 acre pond, walking trail, open-air Clubhouse and Community Pool!
